  <brief_title>Local Anesthetic Infiltration VS Trasversalis Fascia Block VS Spinal Anesthesia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Local Anesthetic Infiltration, Trasversalis Fascia Block or Spinal Anesthesia for Inguinal Hernia Repair</official_title>
  <sponsors>
